  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Access to copyright works for visually impaired people after the transition period
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Cross-border exchanges of accessible format works for visually impaired or otherwise print-disabled people may change.</p>

